---
description: Bank client Python — sigmoid, timing breakdown, padding, slot extraction
globs: bank_client/**/*.py
alwaysApply: false
---

- Use scipy.special.expit for sigmoid, never implement manually
- timing_breakdown dict must have exactly 5 keys matching proto v1.1
- Always pad transactions to 16 before flattening
- Extract slot[k*256] for Depth-1, slot[k*512] for Degree-2
